study_description: The purpose of this project is advance genomic resources for the human immunoglobulin and T cell receptor gene regions. We are constructing additional reference haplotypes for these loci to better existing representations of these complex gene families in current and future builds of the genome reference assembly.
library_generation_protocol: amplification and capture by hybridization of genomic dna to enrich nucleic acid sequences from IG genomic loci
data_processing_protocols: Data was processed using the Igenotyper pipeline (https://github.com/oscarlr/IGenotyper)
